  "title": "Cleaner @ Alps Avenue",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>This role involves maintaining cleanliness and order in office, warehouse, or compound areas to support a safe and efficient work environment.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Clean and maintain office or warehouse areas to ensure hygienic and safe conditions for staff and visitors</li><li>Perform compound cleaning tasks to keep outdoor and surrounding areas tidy and free of debris</li><li>Follow daily cleaning schedules and use appropriate cleaning tools and materials effectively</li><li>Dispose of waste properly to maintain cleanliness and comply with safety standards</li><li>Report any maintenance issues or safety hazards observed during cleaning activities to supervisors promptly</li></ul><p>Working Hours</p><ul><li>Mon to Fri: 7:00 AM – 4:00 PM</li><li>Saturday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 AM</li><li>Working Days: 5.5 days/week</li></ul>",
